---
// Footer Component - Upclub Style
---

<footer class="bg-dark text-white/70 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12">
      <!-- Company Info -->
      <div>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="로잉프로" class="h-12 w-auto brightness-0 invert" />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <p class="text-white font-bold text-base">상호: (주)로잉프로</p>
          <p>대표자: [대표자명]</p>
          <p>주소: [주소]</p>
          <p>전화: [전화번호]</p>
          <p>이메일: [이메일]</p>
          <p>사업자등록번호: [사업자등록번호]</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white text-base font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wide">Quick Links</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div>
            <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-medium">개인정보 처리방침</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-medium">문의하기</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="/about" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-medium">회사 소개</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="/programs" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-medium">프로그램</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Copyright -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8 text-sm text-center">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} ROWINGPRO. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
